Package: ThinkingGrid
Title: Tools for Thinking Grid Statistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Avinash Kulkarni [aut, cph], Vishal Kuvar [aut, cre], Zac Irving [ctb, fnd]
Maintainer: Vishal Kuvar <kuvar001@umn.edu>
